com.isotrol.impe3.pms.gui.api.service
Interface IContentTypesServiceAsync

All Known Implementing Classes:
ContentTypesController
public interface IContentTypesServiceAsync

GWT-RPC service for content types.
It is analog to ContentTypesService, but uses GWT-compatible types.

Author:
Andrei Cojocaru
